Also research Bow Saw and Gold Mining. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/3d/Make-Your-Economy-Boom-in-Age-of-Empires-2-Step-8Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-Your-Economy-Boom-in-Age-of-Empires-2-Step-8Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/3/3d/Make-Your-Economy-Boom-in-Age-of-Empires-2-Step-8Bullet1.jpg/aid1517927-v4-728px-Make-Your-Economy-Boom-in-Age-of-Empires-2-Step-8Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
